594
00:42:50,553 --> 00:42:53,454
Somebody ought to wait
until she inherits it, then marry her...

595
00:42:53,623 --> 00:42:56,319
...and drown her in her bathtub.

596
00:42:57,059 --> 00:43:00,085
Oh, don't worry,
