609
00:43:49,278 --> 00:43:51,508
Find somebody
with less oil in his hair...

610
00:43:51,681 --> 00:43:53,512
...and don't look like he sing
with a band.

611
00:43:53,683 --> 00:43:56,049
Put one of your pals on it.

