641
00:46:18,561 --> 00:46:21,894
I don't know what she do
or don't favor no more.

642
00:46:22,231 --> 00:46:24,199
Not that it matters.

643
00:46:27,570 --> 00:46:32,337
Yeah, I must have poured 10,000
gallons of swill in them troughs.

644
00:46:33,242 --> 00:46:36,040
Still doing it. Pouring swill.

645
00:46:36,212 --> 00:46:38,612
Some things never change.

646
00:46:42,818 --> 00:46:43,807
Hey.

647
00:46:46,722 --> 00:46:49,316
- What's up?
- Judge Irwin.

648
00:46:51,827 --> 00:46:53,454
Judge Irwin what?

649
00:46:54,397 --> 00:46:56,661
- Spill it.
- I'll spill it when I have my breath.

650
00:46:56,832 --> 00:46:59,130
You're using it up
explaining you don't have it.

651
00:46:59,301 --> 00:47:01,929
