00:47:21,524 --> 00:47:23,458
Tiny was figuring
on having supper up here.

659
00:47:23,626 --> 00:47:25,355
Clear them all out.

660
00:47:43,045 --> 00:47:44,478
Which way up there?

661
00:47:46,449 --> 00:47:49,316
Jack, tell Sugar
how to get to the house.

662
00:47:50,319 --> 00:47:52,913
