00:49:45,701 --> 00:49:47,328
It's no exaggeration.

689
00:49:48,470 --> 00:49:50,131
Yeah, I see.

690
00:49:51,473 --> 00:49:53,464
If you're clear on that
and finished with your drink...

691
00:49:53,642 --> 00:49:55,576
...I'd appreciate it
if you'd just get out.

692
00:49:55,744 --> 00:49:58,679
Hey, thank you, judge,
I think I will have just one more spot.

693
00:50:01,550 --> 00:50:05,008
So I see it there in the paper,
and I hear you say it...

694
00:50:05,187 --> 00:50:08,122
...but are you sure
you took it to the Lord in prayer?

695
00:50:08,824 --> 00:50:10,689
