00:50:14,496 --> 00:50:16,964
Because if I recollect right,
I recollect that...

698
00:50:17,132 --> 00:50:19,532
...when we had our conversation
in town that time...

699
00:50:19,702 --> 00:50:23,263
...you sort of felt like what MacMurphy
and his boys were saying about me...

700
00:50:23,539 --> 00:50:24,801
...was beneath contempt.

701
00:50:24,974 --> 00:50:27,772
