00:51:00,376 --> 00:51:03,209
And that's dirt too,
come to think of it.

712
00:51:03,779 --> 00:51:05,440
Dirt makes the grass green...

713
00:51:05,981 --> 00:51:07,539
...let it breathe.

714
00:51:07,716 --> 00:51:11,743
The diamond on my wife's finger
ain't nothing but dirt got awful hot.

715
00:51:11,920 --> 00:51:14,889
What are we, but dirt blowed off
the hands of God almighty?

716
00:51:15,057 --> 00:51:18,083
You and me
and George Washington.

717
00:51:19,995 --> 00:51:21,428
And Jack there.

718
00:51:24,433 --> 00:51:25,730
Still doesn't alter the fact.

719
00:51:25,901 --> 00:51:29,769
I'm not trying to alter anything,
just illuminate it.

720
00:51:31,306 --> 00:51:32,534
Yeah.

721
00:51:32,708 --> 00:51:36,075
You saying MacMurphy and his bunch,
yelling for my impeachment...

722
00:51:36,245 --> 00:51:39,043
...they're responsible,
law-abiding men?

723
00:51:39,314 --> 00:51:42,579
Yeah, they're responsible all right,
