855
01:01:58,900 --> 01:02:01,460
Now, I told you to dig,
not scuff your shoe a little bit.

856
01:02:01,619 --> 01:02:04,952
- You gotta get out and talk to them.
- To whom?

857
01:02:05,423 --> 01:02:07,118
