894
01:04:20,691 --> 01:04:22,716
No. Not anymore.

895
01:04:23,928 --> 01:04:26,920
He took the piano, or someone did.

896
01:04:27,131 --> 01:04:30,430
Took it and put it in that place
he's living. Have you seen it?

897
01:04:32,870 --> 01:04:36,636
God forbid my brother
ever spent any money on himself.

898
01:04:36,974 --> 01:04:39,101
Or that people knew it.

899
01:04:42,547 --> 01:04:44,447
How's your wife?

900
01:04:44,682 --> 01:04:47,742
I'm sorry, I've forgotten her name.

901
01:04:49,187 --> 01:04:51,655
