as I'd hoped.

902
01:04:52,824 --> 01:04:55,418
A lot of tangled bedclothes
and unspoken loathing...

903
01:04:55,593 --> 01:04:57,925
...then spoken loathing
and no tangled bedclothes.

904
01:05:00,364 --> 01:05:03,333
Didn't I read of your engagement
in the society column?

905
01:05:03,501 --> 01:05:07,028
Which you know
I always turn to first in the paper.

906
01:05:07,772 --> 01:05:10,434
I was engaged. More than once.

907
01:05:11,576 --> 01:05:13,043
Adam didn't care for any of them.

908
01:05:14,245 --> 01:05:17,976
- Why that should matter, I don't know.
- Who needs them, anyway?

909
01:05:25,490 --> 01:05:30,427
Anne, way back,
was Judge Irwin ever broke?

910
01:05:31,662 --> 01:05:32,890
What?

911
01:05:33,331 --> 01:05:35,765
Judges don't make
the kind of money your father did...

912
01:05:35,933 --> 01:05:37,798
