or anyone who lives here.

913
01:05:38,503 --> 01:05:41,472
Why on earth would you want
to know such a thing?

914
01:05:41,639 --> 01:05:45,166
- Someone asked me and I didn't know.
- Asked you what?

915
01:05:45,743 --> 01:05:47,643
What I just asked you.

916
01:05:47,812 --> 01:05:49,370
Why?

917
01:05:52,083 --> 01:05:54,074
Oh, Jack,
what are you doing for that man?

918
01:05:54,252 --> 01:05:56,982
- That man.
