from being on his payroll.

923
01:06:09,133 --> 01:06:12,159
- Is it?
- Yes, it is.

924
01:06:17,208 --> 01:06:19,870
- Oh, don't ruin it.
- What?

925
01:06:20,344 --> 01:06:21,971
