942
01:08:14,892 --> 01:08:17,759
Bought out by Georgia Fidelity.

943
01:08:18,162 --> 01:08:20,630
Got any idea
who was president then?

944
01:08:21,365 --> 01:08:23,196
Franklin Roosevelt.

945
01:08:24,635 --> 01:08:28,071
Ma'am, of the bank.

946
